
1.	Hospital (Hospital ID, Name, Address, Phone No)

2.	Drug (Drug ID, Name, Description, Dosage, Expiration Date, Unit Price)

3.	Supplier (Supplier ID, Name, Address, Phone No, Email)

4.	Inventory (Drug ID*, Supplier ID*, Quantity)

5.	Order (Order ID, Hospital ID, Order Date)

6.	Order Detail (Order ID*, Drug ID*, Quantity)

7.	Invoice (Invoice Number, Order ID, Invoice Date)  

*Also, a primary key
